hang out with if the price of entry is (allegedly) $3,000? An AI bot might =
be a solution!

More broadly, nothing in this Update is a prediction about what Apple may o=
r may not do. What is very interesting to me, though, is that while Apple w=
ill absolutely be a winner to the extent that these AI models can run local=
ly, the extent of that victory may be defined by the extent to which the co=
mpany is willing to lean into the =E2=80=9Copen=E2=80=9D part of open sourc=
e: there will be opportunities in the walled garden, a la the AOL of old, b=
ut the largest return may be found in the wildness of the AI-equivalent of =
the world wide web.

